<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: DeYoung</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-08-16 14:11:03</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>35 times, still no Bullsmasher.  Congrats to all you lucky devils!  If you are KOS in the mines, here's a safe path:  go straight in the door (don't stop moving) and follow that hall to a room with only one exit to the left.  Take that exit and take the second right to a "T".  Turn left and go to the room at the end with just that one exit.  Turn around.  Red V spawns in the room opposite on the wall you can see.  Cast or shoot an arrow to pull him to your room.  Don't let him run or he will bring back friends or self destruct on the guard outside the mines.  Good luck!</font></td></tr></table>
